'''Sith Slayer Droids''' were [[Battle droid/Legends|battle droid]] tanks that possessed an organic [[Brain/Legends|brain]] inside. Crafted through [[Sith alchemy/Legends|Sith alchemy]], they were difficult and expensive to produce. Twelve [[Meter/Legends|meters]] in height, the Slayer possessed two shoulder-mounted blaster cannons as well as a single spinning blade on both arms. As a result of the alchemy, they were more capable of shrugging off blows which the [[Sith/Legends|Sith's]] organic warbeasts lacked.

